@startuml
title StreamingToolExecutor Lifecycle

skinparam backgroundColor #F7F1E6
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 135
skinparam ranksep 34
skinparam nodesep 24
skinparam defaultFontName Georgia
skinparam defaultFontSize 15
skinparam TitleFontSize 20
skinparam NoteFontSize 14
skinparam ArrowFontSize 13
skinparam TitleFontColor #161616
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor #F2E9D9
  BorderColor #1D1D1D
  FontColor #161616
  ArrowColor #5E5A53
  StartColor #8C2721
  EndColor #161616
  DiamondBackgroundColor #F5EBDD
  DiamondBorderColor #8C2721
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #F5EBDD
  BorderColor #8C2721
  FontColor #7B1E1E
}

start
:Queued;
:Check canExecuteTool?;
if (eligible?) then (yes)
  :Permission check;
  if (approved?) then (yes)
    :Executing;
    if (progress?) then (progress)
      :Emit progress update;
    endif
    if (completed?) then (done)
      :Completed result ready;
      :Yield in safe order;
    else (aborted)
      :Synthetic error / discard;
    endif
  else (no)
    :Synthetic error;
  endif
else (wait)
  :Wait for promise or progress;
endif
:Yielded;
stop

note right
这里处理的是流式工具状态：
- queued
- executing
- completed
- yielded

并把中断、拒绝、
sibling failure 收成
受控结束语义。
end note

@enduml
